               , Eden-grove, Holloway, gentleman.</p>

               <p>
               
                  <persName id="t18200416-1-person157" type="jurorName">
                     John 
                     Fowler
                  <interp inst="t18200416-1-person157" type="surname" value="Fowler"></interp>
